DRAGON'S LAIR - SINGES CASTLE:
            
        You can play easy mode and still see all the screens.  Select the
        hardest possible setting before starting the game,including
        disabling flip screen and choosing only 3 lives.  Now click on the
        game icon and do as if you were to start the game.  When you are
        prompted to click to play,  just choose exit.  Now select easy mode
        and more lives and away you go.
